Compile the Visualizer:

  make honey

(You need SDL 1.2.x to compile it.)

Run the Visualizer on a board:

  honey -f <board.json>

Keys:
  LEFT_ARROW / RIGHT_ARROW = Move Unit left/right.
  UP_ARROW / DOWN_ARROW = Rotate Unit counter-clockwise/clockwise.
  A / S = Move Unit down left/right.
  Q / ESCAPE = Quit.
